cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.MM

Reasoning: The paper deals with visual relationship detection, which is a task in computer vision. Therefore, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also mentions the use of language modules, which suggests that it may also belong to cs.CL (Computation and Language). Additionally, the paper proposes a sophisticated spatial vector, which could fall under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) or cs.LG (Machine Learning). Finally, the paper evaluates its models on the Visual Relationship Detection and Visual Genome datasets, which could place it under cs.MM (Multimedia).
